Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:43.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}刚刚才穿过那略显寂静的草原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:53.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}便迎来大家沐浴阳光的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:58.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}亲如一家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:01.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}自然而然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:03.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}相守相望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:11.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(280,280)\blur3}采撷点滴温馨 探索奇妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}天空近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:19.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}花儿悄然绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:24.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}静静流淌的日子竟也如此芬芳可爱
